{"type":"text","timestamp":1778614278931,"sessionID":"ses_1e254750effeSqkX9XigYVbMht","part":{"id":"prt_e1dac0829001P9D9Gr73qJP26J","messageID":"msg_e1dabe0dd001u03lBtqnAzFP6a","sessionID":"ses_1e254750effeSqkX9XigYVbMht","type":"text","text":"The micro-opt record is dominated by regressions from added muxing/control; the durable wins were removing rare DIV from the ALU, pruning late control state, valid-only resets, and accepted-fetch replay. I’m going to avoid another frontend predictor/replay expansion and target a small common-path simplification.","time":{"start":1778614274089,"end":1778614278930},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0549321f9ad846a9016a038001f6c4819587da62bb10649c45","phase":"commentary"}}}}
