{"type":"text","timestamp":1778615818343,"sessionID":"ses_1e23d079bffeuSJQ2dbzbV0CwL","part":{"id":"prt_e1dc38ab6001o7RU9JuwqVK7q9","messageID":"msg_e1dc33687001V4kwhpXusPWUfm","sessionID":"ses_1e23d079bffeuSJQ2dbzbV0CwL","type":"text","text":"The log confirms prior micro-opt wins mostly came from pruning timing/routing, while replay-table follow-ups regressed when they added state or changed training. I’m going to target a narrower IF replay mux simplification rather than another predictor or bypass.","time":{"start":1778615814838,"end":1778615818342},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0c667b55fd564295016a038606b8548196a0f8e5ce3adc4279","phase":"commentary"}}}}
