{"type":"text","timestamp":1778606974428,"sessionID":"ses_1e2c4eb7dffefUcGsmRuq4oMSK","part":{"id":"prt_e1d3c8ca9002hLQ6Qe0MUgU17W","messageID":"msg_e1d3b87ee001WhqssRA0nitHPl","sessionID":"ses_1e2c4eb7dffefUcGsmRuq4oMSK","type":"text","text":"The prior successful `micro_opt` changes are both routing/reset-pressure reductions, while predictor, memory-buffer, byte-lane, and multiplier variants repeatedly regressed by adding mux/control depth. I’m going to focus the new hypothesis on another narrow fanout reduction rather than cycle-count speculation.","time":{"start":1778606967977,"end":1778606974427},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_02c93efc92a18983016a036377e190819786b239d23cd8d088","phase":"commentary"}}}}
