{"type":"text","timestamp":1778608920933,"sessionID":"ses_1e2a7c3d0ffetzkVJdQsXFZZ7F","part":{"id":"prt_e1d5a3ed4001xMonzFTdKUeIVB","messageID":"msg_e1d588bc4001nwydC3d8ikZMcF","sessionID":"ses_1e2a7c3d0ffetzkVJdQsXFZZ7F","type":"text","text":"The history favors small Fmax-oriented pruning over anything that adds frontend prediction, memory buffering, or M-unit handshakes. I’m going to target an EX-stage micro-optimization that factors duplicate PC/immediate adders and branch compare logic without changing pipeline timing or IPC.","time":{"start":1778608914132,"end":1778608920931},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0c8c50353e427586016a036b11fd388196a4bc3da56fa2d0ea","phase":"commentary"}}}}
