{"type":"text","timestamp":1778612752780,"sessionID":"ses_1e26f754dffezkQZ4gdYkTnXqa","part":{"id":"prt_e1d94d07f001jbADd0oqIyg484","messageID":"msg_e1d90d64c0011yKBJCwXFM3c6N","sessionID":"ses_1e26f754dffezkQZ4gdYkTnXqa","type":"text","text":"The structural history mostly penalizes added queues, predictors, wider replay tables, and bypass paths. The best new angle is to reuse the successful IF replay table more aggressively by filling it opportunistically during backend stalls, without adding a decode queue or branch-repair metadata.","time":{"start":1778612752511,"end":1778612752779},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0801173a8df234d3016a037a1052b88197a26dab64286d1fd3","phase":"commentary"}}}}
