M instruction bits, and derive\\n16:   the MEM/WB load-result select from mem_read rather than carrying mem_to_reg\\n17:   through ID/EX and EX/MEM. The decoder should still validate every opcode and\\n18:   funct field exactly as today, with is_illegal defaulting high, but it no longer\\n19:   needs to export these simple mirror controls.\\n20: \\n21:   This keeps the five-stage timing, accepted-fetch replay table, NRET=1 RVFI\\n22:   contract, trap semantics, ... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n12: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1778616650977,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e231c63affeCxs3BPM8Ye0FON\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e1dd04ce0001DBadlJrYO39wxf\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"7dee8224c7638b7d863de1978a420a6ea61437d6\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e1dd0339a001dyGuFbOG21B57E\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e231c63affeCxs3BPM8Ye0FON\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":71093,\"input\":6861,\"output\":83,\"reasoning\":149,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":64000}},\"cost\":0}}\n13: {\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1778616652062,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e231c63affeCxs3BPM8Ye0FON\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e1dd0511d001F8LBQDBSN13tPr\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e1dd04cff0012VBlePld3lPoUP\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e231c63affeCxs3BPM8Ye0FON\",\"snapshot\":\"7dee8224c7638b7d863de1978a420a6ea61437d6\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n14: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1778616655931,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e231c63affeCxs3BPM8Ye0FON\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e1dd05f66001SVrswSZHNeOfey\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e1dd04cff0012VBlePld3lPoUP\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e231c63affeCxs3BPM8Ye0FON\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Wrote the hypothesis YAML to `cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260512-001-r15s0.yaml`.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1778616655718,\"end\":1778616655929},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"msg_06849d87cb3b12b8016a03894f9b888198ae847baeef772c04\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}}}}\n15: {\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1778616656013,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e231c63affeCxs3BPM8Ye0