{"type":"text","timestamp":1778596662442,"sessionID":"ses_1e36402c1ffeWw0UF74O8zUKWR","part":{"id":"prt_e1c9f3827001hzx38d359469aS","messageID":"msg_e1c9c7192001WIzIEOSKYdXiQS","sessionID":"ses_1e36402c1ffeWw0UF74O8zUKWR","type":"text","text":"Prior structural work already tried a broad M-unit split and failed on multi-cycle handshake correctness. I’m going to propose a different structural angle: decouple fetch from decode with a small instruction skid/prefetch queue so backend stalls can overlap future instruction fetches without adding IF predecode critical-path logic.","time":{"start":1778596657191,"end":1778596662441},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0b8566938cae46de016a033b3103008197ada51aa834d8ba56","phase":"commentary"}}}}
