{"type":"text","timestamp":1778610391023,"sessionID":"ses_1e292bc96ffeAG62aE3Q2RW4S8","part":{"id":"prt_e1d70c215001gk3ALogh8oK6a3","messageID":"msg_e1d6dbb8e001Jjy1QbU3Dc211p","sessionID":"ses_1e292bc96ffeAG62aE3Q2RW4S8","type":"text","text":"The prior predictor record is consistently negative when prediction touches the normal fetch next-PC path. I’m going to write a deliberately narrow predictor hypothesis that avoids IF predecode/tables and predicts only already-resolved sequential post-redirect flow.","time":{"start":1778610389525,"end":1778610391022},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0038d16c34631d91016a0370d543b881958f3a63078aff23d8","phase":"commentary"}}}}
