{"type":"text","timestamp":1778615796269,"sessionID":"ses_1e23d072affeiVe1OxOaRo7RM8","part":{"id":"prt_e1dc340280028ooANZcM0J88Qb","messageID":"msg_e1dc32adb001jJaqpCh0US79Ne","sessionID":"ses_1e23d072affeiVe1OxOaRo7RM8","type":"text","text":"The history strongly disfavors target/branch predictors on this core. The best predictor slot is to stay with instruction replay, but change only the replacement behavior rather than add lookup width, target repair metadata, or frontend predecode.","time":{"start":1778615795752,"end":1778615796269},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0a2cfe6134d42bc5016a0385f385d08195930e83e72f77816f","phase":"commentary"}}}}
