{"type":"text","timestamp":1778602336799,"sessionID":"ses_1e30c4a97ffeALfMMhd3mXamvF","part":{"id":"prt_e1cf5e1c8001PEKyIJS8dTGnen","messageID":"msg_e1cf40974001L4wmVsZkBFP9h3","sessionID":"ses_1e30c4a97ffeALfMMhd3mXamvF","type":"text","text":"Prior predictor attempts all lost mainly by putting target generation, tag lookup, or return decode on the fetch next-PC path. I’m going to write a deliberately narrow predictor hypothesis that keeps the idea in the diversity slot but lowers expected impact and confidence.","time":{"start":1778602336712,"end":1778602336798},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0624b874f73e8fc4016a03516095b081909141b375f24f9f02","phase":"commentary"}}}}
