saturating counters. Carry predicted next-PC metadata with the instruction\n  so EX redirects only on mismatch and updates or clears the entry from the\n  resolved branch.\n\n  This intentionally accepts occasional low-bit alias mispredictions because\n  they are corrected precisely at EX, while making the IF critical-path addition","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/hyp-20260512-003-r5s2.yaml","time":{"start":1778602414159,"end":1778602414162}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_075a207143891512016a0351adaa2c8194b4c5351f6ee8f44d"}},"id":"prt_e1cf70f09001PXgPZcDejyAa9H","sessionID":"ses_1e30c4a97ffeALfMMhd3mXamvF","messageID":"msg_e1cf6ee75001Cui2gBKXs4tK2P"}}
